# Secrets & sensitive data

**Never commit:**
- `.env`, `.env.local`, `appsettings.*.local.json`, `appsettings.Production.json`
- API keys, tokens, certificates (`*.pem`, `*.pfx`, `*.key`)
- User-generated exports (`*.xlsx`, `exports/`)

**Safe to commit:** `frontend/.env.example` (placeholders only), `appsettings.json` (localhost CORS only).

If adding new env vars, update `.env.example` with dummy values and document in `README.md`.

User financial inputs are not persisted server-side; keep it that way unless product scope explicitly adds accounts/storage with privacy policy.
